1
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:16,309
[Tangjing]

2
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,280
We split up.

3
00:00:30,190 --> 00:00:31,760
You go find out where everyone is.

4
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,270
I'll enter the palace to see the Empress

5
00:00:33,270 --> 00:00:35,000
and try to find out something about Li Ce.

6
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,800
The Empress is deeply inscrutable.

7
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,060
Be careful on your own.

8
00:00:42,730 --> 00:00:46,400
[Qingfen Restaurant]

9
00:02:05,890 --> 00:02:11,000
[REBIRTH]

10
00:02:11,510 --> 00:02:14,070
[Episode 17]

11
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,120
I'm Princess Fu.

12
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:20,010
I'd like to request an audience
with Her Majesty.

13
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:23,060
[Linrui Palace]

14
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,860
Greetings, Your Majesty.

15
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,030
Chun'er?

16
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:53,050
I've been expecting you
for quite some time.

17
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:56,190
But I'm afraid
you can no longer call me "Chun'er."

18
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,840
You should address me as
"Princess Consort of Luo."

19
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,040
Where is Her Majesty?

20
00:03:00,250 --> 00:03:01,780
She doesn't want to see you.

21
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:03,520
She sent me in her place.

22
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,310
In that case,

23
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,880
I shall take my leave.

24
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,280
Why the rush?

25
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:10,650
You're about to be married off
to Great Yan as its Queen.

26
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:14,890
I've had some fine wine
specially prepared for you.

27
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,910
Why don't we celebrate first?

28
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,400
Think of it

29
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:20,710
as an early toast
to your upcoming wedding.

30
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:21,640
What did you say?

31
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,180
Queen of Great Yan.

32
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:35,030
Don't you know?

33
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:38,000
Yan Xun has come here
to seek your hand in marriage,

34
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,960
and Her Majesty has already approved.

35
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,910
Your dowry

36
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:43,360
has already been sent to
the Crown Prince's Mansion.

37
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,240
You don't need to
worry about Li Ce anymore.

38
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,650
You may not become
Crown Princess of Biantang,

39
00:03:47,650 --> 00:03:51,050
but very soon
you'll be Queen of Great Yan.

40
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,190
Come on.

41
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,290
Let me teach you.

42
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,960
On your wedding night,
drink the crossed-cup wine

43
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,310
with Yan Xun like this.

44
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:08,790
This is how the Prince of Luo and I
did it.

45
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:14,710
The idea of marrying me off to Great Yan—

46
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:16,490
that was your suggestion.

47
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:18,240
Quite clever of you.

48
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,519
Aren't you going to thank me?

49
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:24,430
You and Yan Xun are so deeply in love.

50
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,070
For your sake,

51
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,750
he cut off the hand of Li Qi, Biantang's

52
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,070
General of Cavalry.

53
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,240
Tell me,

54
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,070
whose tab does that hand go on—

55
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,190
Yan Xun's or yours?

56
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:38,190
Yan Xun is brutal and bloodthirsty.

57
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,920
He's unfit to rule Great Yan.

58
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:41,200
And what about Li Ce?

59
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,360
He was meant to live in luxury
as Crown Prince.

60
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,920
Had you not fought against the Empress
on his behalf,

61
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,920
how would he have ended up like this?

62
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,000
Chun'er,

63
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,870
I know you carry much hatred and pain

64
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,070
in your heart.

65
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:55,310
And you've endured things
you shouldn't have.

66
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,750
But if you remain stuck in the past,

67
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:59,409
you'll only sink deeper into it
and suffer more.

68
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,480
I never understood

69
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,390
why I hated you so much.

70
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,240
I think

71
00:05:09,450 --> 00:05:11,210
it must be out of jealousy.

72
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,630
It's over now.

73
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,310
They're all dead!

74
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,390
I'll take you out of here.

75
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:17,450
I'll take you home!

76
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:18,980
I'll kill you!

77
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,560
I'll kill you!

78
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,510
I'm sorry.

79
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:32,230
I hate you. I hate you! I hate you!

80
00:05:32,260 --> 00:05:33,670
I hate you!

81
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,680
They're all dead!

82
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,310
You killed them all!

83
00:05:38,170 --> 00:05:38,850
Chun'er!

84
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,170
Don't be afraid!

85
00:05:54,090 --> 00:05:56,409
I was born a noble and precious princess.

86
00:05:57,890 --> 00:05:59,490
I seemed to have everything,

87
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,840
but in fact, I have nothing.

88
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:07,800
Even my father's love for me is fake.

89
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,270
You were nothing but a slave,

90
00:06:10,290 --> 00:06:11,950
yet here you stand above us all,

91
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:13,680
with everything I ever wanted.

92
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,390
I just want to see you suffer
with my own eyes—

93
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,870
to watch you lose everything

94
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,560
and everyone you care about!

95
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,370
You're blessed with

96
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,240
a beauty everyone envies.

97
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:29,010
You could've lived a much better life.

98
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:30,480
I know

99
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,340
you feel that Yan Xun and I
have made you suffer.

100
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:35,070
Your mother and your father—

101
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,750
you think they've wronged you too.

102
00:06:36,750 --> 00:06:39,880
You think fate and this world
have treated you unfairly.

103
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,040
You believe you were born to
live in luxury

104
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,480
and stand above the masses.

105
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,120
But that was a gift from fate.

106
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:46,690
You didn't cherish it.

107
00:06:46,690 --> 00:06:48,240
Instead, you chose to use it for revenge—

108
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,840
revenge against me, a slave,

109
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:50,909
against Yan Xun,

110
00:06:51,190 --> 00:06:52,450
and against everyone,

111
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,070
including yourself.

112
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,600
Was it worth it?

113
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:04,600
Yes!

114
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:09,270
I just hate you.

115
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:12,480
I want revenge on you.

116
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,870
Please drink less of my wedding wine,
Princess Consort of Luo.

117
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,870
Too much wine is bad for your health.

118
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,220
The members of the delegation...

119
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,250
were seized by the Empress.

120
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,630
Only Baze and I managed to escape.

121
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,240
I asked Baze...

122
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:15,840
to go to

123
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,910
Ximeng

124
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,470
to deliver a message.

125
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:20,960
Lingyue.

126
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:30,030
How are things with Li Ce?

127
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:33,160
He's indeed in prison.

128
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:36,550
Lin Mu and Song Cheng were also captured
along with him.

129
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:38,150
On the day it happened,

130
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:41,000
I wasn't at the restaurant,
so I avoided it.

131
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,860
They knew you would never abandon
the Crown Prince.

132
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:45,810
It was all just to lure you back.

133
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:46,950
[Mihe Abode]

134
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,300
Your Highness!

135
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,860
Your Highness,

136
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:55,390
there is a carriage
from Great Yan outside.

137
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:57,190
They say they're here to see you.

138
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,630
Chu.

139
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:28,940
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

140
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:31,640
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

141
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:32,200
Chu.

142
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:33,050
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

143
00:10:33,070 --> 00:10:34,550
♪ My longing surges ♪

144
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:37,170
♪ I become haggard ♪

145
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,970
These are my old clothes
from when I was the Heir Apparent.

146
00:10:37,970 --> 00:10:39,920
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

147
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:40,350
I didn't expect them to still fit.

148
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:42,770
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

149
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:41,840
Chu,

150
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,840
I especially put on this outfit today

151
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,770
♪ My love remains ♪

152
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,510
because I wanted to see you
in this identity.

153
00:10:44,990 --> 00:10:48,520
♪ But you're already gone ♪

154
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,390
Right now, I'm not the King of Great Yan.

155
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:50,670
I'm just a hostage prince
trapped in Zhenhuangcheng.

156
00:10:48,770 --> 00:10:50,390
♪ What I seek in life ♪

157
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:52,200
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

158
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,670
Chu,

159
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:54,270
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

160
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,750
could you, even if just for a moment,

161
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:56,290
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

162
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,870
be the slave Chu Qiao
trapped in Qingshan Manor?

163
00:10:56,580 --> 00:10:59,770
♪ My longing still rests ♪

164
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,630
I want to take you somewhere.

165
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:02,140
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

166
00:11:02,260 --> 00:11:03,840
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

167
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:06,350
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

168
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:11,000
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

169
00:11:11,370 --> 00:11:12,720
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

170
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:15,010
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

171
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:17,460
♪ How do we start over? ♪

172
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:20,400
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

173
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:23,170
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

174
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:26,120
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

175
00:11:26,150 --> 00:11:29,070
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

176
00:11:29,090 --> 00:11:31,820
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

177
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:34,240
♪ In the end ♪

178
00:11:52,160 --> 00:11:53,320
-Make way!
-Make way!

179
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,780
-Make way!
-Out of the way!

180
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,720
Who has the nerve to block the city gate?

181
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,380
Arrest her!

182
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,670
I'm the Consort of the King of Great Yan.

183
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:06,000
Take me to see him.

184
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,660
Consort of Great Yan?

185
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:09,190
Hurry! Prepare a carriage!

186
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:12,360
-Prepare a carriage!
-Prepare a carriage!

187
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:17,130
Make way!

188
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,090
Make way!

189
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:50,150
Why did you bring me here?

190
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,120
This ribbon

191
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:59,920
is part of a tradition among the people
of Mount Huihui in Great Yan.

192
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:00,850
When I was young,

193
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:03,390
my mother often stayed there.

194
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:04,910
She told me

195
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:07,310
that the people of Mount Huihui
in Great Yan

196
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:09,200
would hang this ribbon,

197
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,600
along with this wishing plaque...

198
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:15,320
on this wishing tree.

199
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:16,870
Then the wind

200
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:20,270
would carry their wishes
high into the sky,

201
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:22,640
and their wishes could come true.

202
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,440
Chu.

203
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,610
Forget our pain and sorrow.

204
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,900
Come back to Great Yan with me.

205
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,510
I once promised you

206
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:47,950
that Great Yan

207
00:13:48,550 --> 00:13:49,950
will always be your home.

208
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:51,650
Chu,

209
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,840
we used to be so close

210
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,300
that we could entrust our lives
to each other.

211
00:13:56,300 --> 00:13:57,200
After losing you,

212
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:59,460
it feels as though I lost the whole world.

213
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,850
Only if you come back

214
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:03,270
can I find myself again.

215
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:09,920
Yan Xun,

216
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:11,630
I know you

217
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,360
just as you know me.

218
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:20,410
Chu?

219
00:14:21,020 --> 00:14:22,590
Stop pretending.

220
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:23,810
What you feel for me

221
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:27,030
is nothing more than a desire
to conquer and possess.

222
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:29,090
If you truly had any affection for me,

223
00:14:29,390 --> 00:14:30,270
Miss Zhong,

224
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:32,240
those people
from the Universal Harmony Guild,

225
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,200
and Huan Huan

226
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:36,100
would not have died by your sword.

227
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,170
Zhao Chun'er was right.

228
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:39,200
My mistake

229
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:42,600
was believing in your feelings back then.

230
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:46,630
Now I'll correct that mistake
with my own hands.

231
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,550
Chu,

232
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:51,940
can you really bring yourself to kill me?

233
00:14:52,790 --> 00:14:54,630
If you truly wanted to,

234
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:58,200
you would've done it by the frozen lake.

235
00:15:13,450 --> 00:15:14,900
You poisoned me...

236
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,510
Don't worry, Chu.

237
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,560
Just some sedative incense
that suppresses your inner power.

238
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:22,820
It will wear off on its own
within an hour.

239
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:25,240
Don't try my patience.

240
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:26,870
You're right.

241
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,150
You know me

242
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:30,870
just as I know you.

243
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,960
That's why I made preparations in advance.

244
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,720
I can kill you anytime.

245
00:15:40,170 --> 00:15:40,800
However,

246
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:43,080
I won't kill you.

247
00:15:43,850 --> 00:15:45,360
Three days from now, I want you

248
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,240
to appear at the gates
of the Crown Prince's Mansion

249
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,840
wearing the bridal robes
of the Queen of Great Yan.

250
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:50,650
Otherwise,

251
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:54,040
I'll destroy everything you hold dear.

252
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,030
That Crown Prince of Biantang,

253
00:15:58,120 --> 00:16:00,030
anyone who follows you,
or anyone you care about—

254
00:16:00,030 --> 00:16:01,480
I will spare none of them.

255
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:03,660
I'll make every single one

256
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:04,910
of them

257
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:08,480
wish they were dead.

258
00:16:12,690 --> 00:16:14,990
[King of Great Yan's Travelling Residence]

259
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:29,980
Your Majesty.

260
00:16:30,340 --> 00:16:31,200
What happened?

261
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,590
Come with me quickly.

262
00:16:47,730 --> 00:16:48,580
Your Majesty.

263
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:03,270
Consort Helian

264
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:05,930
was brought here
by the guards at Yingtian Gate.

265
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:08,230
They said she fainted at the city gate

266
00:17:08,230 --> 00:17:10,230
because she had ridden for too long,

267
00:17:11,170 --> 00:17:13,930
traveling day and night without rest,
leaving her body weakened.

268
00:17:13,930 --> 00:17:15,200
Why did she come here?

269
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:16,270
Most likely, she heard

270
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:18,730
that Your Majesty is going to
marry Queen Chu

271
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:20,510
and panicked.

272
00:17:25,829 --> 00:17:26,630
Your Majesty.

273
00:17:32,430 --> 00:17:33,230
Your Majesty.

274
00:17:34,910 --> 00:17:36,770
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

275
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,640
I know I was wrong.

276
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:58,680
I know

277
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:01,060
Your Majesty loves Queen Chu.

278
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:04,110
I would never dare compete with her
for your affection,

279
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:06,270
nor would I do anything to harm her.

280
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:07,940
I was just afraid...

281
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:12,990
afraid that once Your Majesty marries her,

282
00:18:14,390 --> 00:18:15,780
you would abandon me.

283
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:18,510
I only beg Your Majesty
not to send me away.

284
00:18:18,590 --> 00:18:22,200
Let me stay and serve you and Queen Chu.

285
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:26,680
Your Majesty!

286
00:18:29,090 --> 00:18:29,810
Cheng Yuan.

287
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:33,040
Consort Helian is injured.

288
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,970
Find two maids to attend to her.

289
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:36,660
Yes.

290
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,030
What do you think Zhuge Yue

291
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:23,430
means by bringing back
a woman from Ximeng?

292
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:27,200
This courtyard was left to Princess Fu
by the Crown Prince.

293
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:29,060
The Princess told us to meet here.

294
00:19:29,510 --> 00:19:30,240
But look at him—

295
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:32,500
he brought back some ugly foreign woman.

296
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:39,240
What are you doing?

297
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:39,880
Stop it!

298
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:43,250
I'm thinking of a way
to rescue the Crown Prince.

299
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,160
You...

300
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:45,880
Wang Shi'er,

301
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,290
why don't you dig a tunnel right here

302
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:49,210
and dig His Highness out?

303
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:51,170
How about that?

304
00:19:51,310 --> 00:19:52,910
That's the Imperial Prison—

305
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:55,030
the most secure prison in this country.

306
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:57,490
Tight security
isn't the only problem here.

307
00:19:57,680 --> 00:19:58,740
Bad news! Bad news!

308
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:01,130
Miss Chu is going to be married off
to Great Yan!

309
00:20:01,130 --> 00:20:02,060
What did you say?

310
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:04,840
Miss Chu is being married off
to Great Yan!

311
00:20:05,910 --> 00:20:07,770
-"Married off?"
-"Married off?"

312
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,680
Could it be that the Princess plans to
use this marriage

313
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:12,750
to call on Great Yan's Black Eagle Army
to save His Highness?

314
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:14,350
I actually think this method could work.

315
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:15,280
It's worth a try.

316
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,440
At a time like this,

317
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,680
you're still in the mood to joke?

318
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:18,750
How else could it be?

319
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:21,640
How could the Princess possibly agree to
some marriage alliance?

320
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:23,170
What are you talking about?

321
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:28,260
Young Master,

322
00:20:28,350 --> 00:20:30,270
did you know Yan Xun is going to
marry Miss Chu?

323
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:33,530
The Biantang Empress has already issued
a decree for this.

324
00:20:33,890 --> 00:20:35,680
I heard about it on my way here.

325
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:36,880
Aren't you worried?

326
00:20:37,290 --> 00:20:39,480
I'd just intended to go to
the Crown Prince's Mansion to see Miss Chu,

327
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,440
but I heard that early this morning,

328
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,640
she went out with Yan Xun

329
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,910
and hasn't returned yet.

330
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:44,910
Didn't we agree to meet here?

331
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,680
But it's been two days.

332
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:47,800
Miss Chu...

333
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:57,690
I just went to the Imperial Prison

334
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,480
to find a way to see Li Ce.

335
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,220
However, the Empress has given her orders.

336
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:02,550
No one dared to let me in.

337
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:05,200
Li Ce is currently charged with
regicide and treason.

338
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,480
Naturally, the Empress
has countless reasons

339
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,750
to bar anyone from seeing him.

340
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:08,990
If I'm not mistaken,

341
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:11,720
her next move will likely be to use Li Ce

342
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:12,750
to force you to leave here.

343
00:21:12,750 --> 00:21:15,010
You know that I'm to marry into Great Yan?

344
00:21:15,790 --> 00:21:17,350
This is the Empress's scheme.

345
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,810
If we want to save Li Ce now,

346
00:21:19,030 --> 00:21:20,640
we can only clear his name.

347
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,750
The case of
the Crown Prince assassinating the Emperor

348
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:24,790
is riddled with
suspicious inconsistencies.

349
00:21:24,790 --> 00:21:26,480
The assassin took his own life on the spot

350
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,940
after the attempt failed.

351
00:21:28,310 --> 00:21:31,110
We have no way to begin
if we wish to reopen the case.

352
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:36,070
I know where the assassin's body is.

353
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,720
The death row inmates
and felons in Tangjing,

354
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:39,550
after death, are all buried

355
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:41,470
outside a fir grove
in the west of the city.

356
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:42,930
That place is a mass grave.

357
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:44,160
I can take you there.

358
00:21:50,710 --> 00:21:51,440
General Sun.

359
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,270
General Sun.

360
00:21:58,770 --> 00:21:59,900
General Sun.

361
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:02,920
What brings you here, General Sun?

362
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:03,920
Someone,

363
00:22:03,950 --> 00:22:05,200
serve tea to General Sun.

364
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:05,760
No need.

365
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:06,830
Lord Zuo,

366
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:09,000
I came today for a case file.

367
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:11,030
Give it to me, and I'll be on my way.

368
00:22:11,030 --> 00:22:12,960
I won't keep you from your fine tea.

369
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:14,640
What kind of file

370
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,920
is important enough for you
to come in person?

371
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:17,720
You could've simply

372
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,960
sent someone here.

373
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:22,690
The case of the assassination attempt
on His Majesty a few days ago.

374
00:22:25,360 --> 00:22:26,090
General Sun,

375
00:22:26,340 --> 00:22:28,770
this file was taken by the higher-ups.

376
00:22:30,790 --> 00:22:31,480
Then...

377
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,070
I'll take my leave.

378
00:22:33,550 --> 00:22:35,080
Sorry for the disturbance.

379
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:36,730
Take care, General Sun.

380
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:45,070
Go report to Lord Zhan.

381
00:22:46,830 --> 00:22:48,830
Tell him that General Sun came here.

382
00:22:49,380 --> 00:22:49,940
Yes.

383
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:02,790
Didn't Xiao Ran say
her injuries weren't severe?

384
00:23:02,790 --> 00:23:05,510
Why hasn't she woken up
after a whole day and night?

385
00:23:05,510 --> 00:23:07,000
Although her current injuries
are not severe,

386
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:09,310
her old wounds haven't fully healed yet.

387
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:10,910
On top of that,

388
00:23:11,500 --> 00:23:13,000
her body has long been worn out.

389
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:14,160
New injuries compounding old wounds—

390
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:16,220
that's why she's still unconscious.

391
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,150
Isn't she the Queen of the Lingyue Clan?

392
00:23:30,150 --> 00:23:31,960
Why does she have so many old wounds?

393
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:34,960
Even the spies of Qingshan Manor
didn't have this many scars.

394
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,770
After the Lingyue Clan was conquered
by King Ximeng,

395
00:23:36,770 --> 00:23:38,770
she was nothing more than his slave.

396
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:42,000
Many of the things she did
were not of her own choosing.

397
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:43,680
Do you remember what Qingshan Manor

398
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:44,720
used to be like?

399
00:23:45,510 --> 00:23:47,710
Ximeng is like a larger Qingshan Manor—

400
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:50,160
or an even crueler one.

401
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,560
Although she's from Ximeng,

402
00:23:53,070 --> 00:23:54,870
she fell into the Empress's trap

403
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:56,880
because she was helping me save He Xiao.

404
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,750
No matter what,

405
00:23:58,270 --> 00:24:00,730
I must make sure
she leaves Biantang safely.

406
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,090
This is the mass grave.

407
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,830
In Tangjing,

408
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:36,070
criminals executed for their crimes,

409
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,750
along with unclaimed bodies,

410
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,440
are sent to be buried here.

411
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:41,510
According to the rules,
the assassin's body

412
00:24:41,510 --> 00:24:42,680
should be somewhere nearby.

413
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:43,640
Let's search the mounds one by one.

414
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,270
No need.

415
00:24:44,450 --> 00:24:45,240
He was buried not long ago.

416
00:24:45,240 --> 00:24:47,250
We can just check the color of the dirt,

417
00:24:47,250 --> 00:24:48,850
and we'll find it right away.

418
00:24:49,430 --> 00:24:50,080
Let's go.

419
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,920
Sorry for the disturbance. Sorry.

420
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,750
Sorry, sorry.

421
00:24:57,930 --> 00:24:59,410
Please don't blame me.

422
00:24:59,790 --> 00:25:01,830
Sorry for the disturbance.

423
00:25:02,750 --> 00:25:04,270
Didn't you say you don't believe in
this sort of thing?

424
00:25:04,270 --> 00:25:05,270
Why are you bowing?

425
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:06,440
The graves I used to rob

426
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:08,310
all belonged to nobles and aristocrats—

427
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:10,720
even the lowest-ranking among them
were third-rank officials.

428
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:11,440
There isn't

429
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:12,900
even a decent coffin here.

430
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:14,920
I'm afraid of being haunted
by some ghosts of paupers,

431
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,380
so I'm paying my respects.

432
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:19,450
Sorry for the disturbance.

433
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:20,750
The burial mounds in this area

434
00:25:20,750 --> 00:25:22,070
are all from long ago.

435
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:25,080
The soil has settled into
thick, distinct layers.

436
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:27,740
Only this one shows no signs
of being disturbed.

437
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:30,270
This mound here is looser.

438
00:25:30,750 --> 00:25:32,070
It looks newly dug.

439
00:25:33,830 --> 00:25:34,630
What's wrong?

440
00:25:36,550 --> 00:25:37,340
The soil has already dried,

441
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:38,590
and the smell of blood has faded.

442
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:40,200
It should be from about a month ago.

443
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:41,860
Not the one we are looking for.

444
00:25:59,550 --> 00:26:00,370
What are you doing?

445
00:26:00,370 --> 00:26:01,970
It's not often I come across someone
in my line of work.

446
00:26:01,970 --> 00:26:02,960
I thought I'd exchange some pointers
with him.

447
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:05,090
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

448
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:08,070
Find a place to hide.

449
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,160
Stay out of sight

450
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,020
and be careful.

451
00:26:24,310 --> 00:26:25,510
Darn it.

452
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,680
It's completely charred.

453
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,240
What can I find out from this?

454
00:26:39,830 --> 00:26:41,200
Why are there three people here?

455
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,720
Which one is Sun Di?

456
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,830
I can't tell.

457
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:46,170
Let's kill all three of them, then.

458
00:26:53,430 --> 00:26:54,270
General Sun.

459
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:55,110
Princess Fu?

460
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,200
Why are you here?

461
00:26:56,490 --> 00:26:58,590
I assume we're all here
on account of the Crown Prince.

462
00:26:58,590 --> 00:27:00,390
The assassin's body is charred.

463
00:27:01,010 --> 00:27:02,210
It's pointless now.

464
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:03,830
No.

465
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:04,820
It's a trap.

466
00:27:22,270 --> 00:27:22,920
Speak.

467
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,310
Who sent you?

468
00:27:24,350 --> 00:27:25,070
Lord Zhan!

469
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,320
Lord Zhan sent us!

470
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:28,000
Then there's no need to keep them alive.

471
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,330
We should kill them all.

472
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,960
-No!
-Don't kill me!

473
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,110
-Spare us!
-Please spare us!

474
00:27:32,110 --> 00:27:33,140
-Don't!
-Please spare us!

475
00:27:33,140 --> 00:27:34,180
Spare us!

476
00:27:42,050 --> 00:27:43,680
Hurry! Run!

477
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:02,750
Greetings, Miss Chu.

478
00:28:04,860 --> 00:28:05,690
General Sun,

479
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:07,000
I'm Princess Fu.

480
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:09,030
You don't need to hide who you really are.

481
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:11,200
When I accompanied the Crown Prince
on a diplomatic mission to Great Yong,

482
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,800
I saw you in Zhenhuangcheng.

483
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:14,350
You might not remember me,

484
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:16,230
but you left a deep impression on me.

485
00:28:16,230 --> 00:28:18,960
You were the martial arts instructor
for Great Yong's imperial guards.

486
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:19,880
So,

487
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,590
you've known who I am all this time.

488
00:28:21,590 --> 00:28:23,070
But you never went to
the Emperor or the Empress

489
00:28:23,070 --> 00:28:24,330
to reveal my identity.

490
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:26,310
It was just a suspicion at first,

491
00:28:26,830 --> 00:28:29,560
but crossing blades with you today
confirmed it.

492
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:31,560
I'd thought that
when the Crown Prince fell into trouble,

493
00:28:31,560 --> 00:28:33,240
you would take the opportunity
to slip away.

494
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:34,500
But I didn't expect you

495
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:36,880
to risk your life for the Crown Prince.

496
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:40,110
I truly admire
your deep affection for him.

497
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:43,980
General Sun, you misunderstand.

498
00:28:43,980 --> 00:28:45,370
His Highness once
showed me great kindness,

499
00:28:45,370 --> 00:28:46,630
so naturally I must...

500
00:28:47,120 --> 00:28:49,250
I naturally understand what you mean.

501
00:28:49,300 --> 00:28:50,450
After all, gratitude

502
00:28:50,450 --> 00:28:52,520
is often where love takes root.

503
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:57,400
Although His Highness once behaved
rather frivolously toward you,

504
00:28:57,570 --> 00:28:59,030
time reveals a person's true character.

505
00:28:59,030 --> 00:29:01,070
I trust that after enduring hardship

506
00:29:01,070 --> 00:29:02,640
side by side with you,

507
00:29:03,110 --> 00:29:05,400
His Highness must be
deeply in love with you.

508
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:08,860
I look forward to raising a glass
at your wedding in the future.

509
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,040
General Sun,

510
00:29:13,310 --> 00:29:15,790
you just said
you came for the Crown Prince today.

511
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:18,020
Does that mean you also believe
there is something suspicious about this?

512
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:19,950
Yes. I was just about to get to that.

513
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:22,900
The day
after His Majesty was assassinated,

514
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:24,850
I happened to be
at the Ministry of Justice.

515
00:29:24,850 --> 00:29:26,920
I didn't want to bring it up
to anyone again,

516
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:29,440
but since it concerns the Crown Prince,

517
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:30,800
I won't hide it anymore.

518
00:29:31,280 --> 00:29:33,310
Fifteen years ago, when I was ordered

519
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:36,240
to suppress the Nanxi Tribe
in the southwest of Biantang,

520
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,500
I had seen that tattoo.

521
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:38,590
The Nanxi people?

522
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:39,200
Yes.

523
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,380
The Nanxi Tribe

524
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:42,740
lived in the mountains west of Biantang.

525
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:43,950
Their land was barren

526
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:45,280
and not suited for farming,

527
00:29:45,280 --> 00:29:49,100
so they frequently raided the borderlands
of Biantang for goods and valuables.

528
00:29:49,100 --> 00:29:51,430
His Majesty ordered me to drive them away.

529
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:53,200
Though few in number,

530
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:55,140
they were cunning and fierce.

531
00:29:55,990 --> 00:29:58,880
After several clashes,
we still couldn't defeat them.

532
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,830
To relieve His Majesty's worries,
Her Majesty

533
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:02,090
issued a secret edict,

534
00:30:02,290 --> 00:30:05,760
ordering me to set fire
to the Nanxi Tribe's villages.

535
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:16,730
General Sun,

536
00:30:16,790 --> 00:30:18,680
we've already sealed off the only exits

537
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,750
of the nearby villages with fire.

538
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:21,270
It should be hard for anyone to escape.

539
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:22,590
Should we stay here and keep watch

540
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:24,390
or leave after the fire goes out?

541
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,830
Let's go. No need to keep watch.

542
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:31,400
The Nanxi people lived in wooden buildings
for generations.

543
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:34,030
Once the fire started,
it spread through everything.

544
00:30:34,030 --> 00:30:34,920
After that day,

545
00:30:35,590 --> 00:30:37,720
very few Nanxi people survived.

546
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:40,790
The entire tribe vanished after that.

547
00:30:41,900 --> 00:30:44,100
I didn't want to carry out such an order,

548
00:30:44,170 --> 00:30:46,500
but I had no choice
but to obey the Empress.

549
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:47,650
So you're saying

550
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:51,080
that the tattoo is the Nanxi Tribe's mark,

551
00:30:51,510 --> 00:30:54,350
and the assassin was a Nanxi survivor?

552
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:57,920
The Nanxi Tribe was wiped out
over 10 years ago.

553
00:30:58,350 --> 00:30:59,720
For one to suddenly appear now

554
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:02,000
and be claimed to
have acted on the Crown Prince's orders—

555
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,530
that simply does not add up.

556
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:05,680
Miss Chu,

557
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:08,110
you've spent day and night
at the Crown Prince's side,

558
00:31:08,110 --> 00:31:09,570
closer to him than anyone.

559
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:11,340
You must believe more than I do

560
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:13,170
that the Crown Prince couldn't possibly
have had any connection

561
00:31:13,170 --> 00:31:14,830
with the Nanxi people, right?

562
00:31:17,120 --> 00:31:18,720
Why are you always coughing?

563
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,920
Miss, who is this?

564
00:31:21,670 --> 00:31:22,540
He is...

565
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:23,440
A guard.

566
00:31:25,810 --> 00:31:26,650
A guard?

567
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:28,090
I'm General Chu's guard,

568
00:31:28,780 --> 00:31:30,520
responsible for her safety.

569
00:31:34,590 --> 00:31:36,920
When I crossed blades with you earlier
in the mass grave,

570
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:39,070
I could tell you were quite skilled.

571
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,580
Are you interested

572
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:45,000
in taking a post in our Tang Army?

573
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:50,880
You don't need to look at the Princess.

574
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:52,550
No matter how much she pays you,

575
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:54,880
I'll pay three times as much.
How about it?

576
00:31:56,430 --> 00:31:57,020
Zhu...

577
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:00,070
Guard,

578
00:32:00,250 --> 00:32:01,380
what do you think?

579
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:06,730
Thank you for your appreciation,
General Sun.

580
00:32:06,730 --> 00:32:09,800
However, I'm not only
the Princess's guard,

581
00:32:10,790 --> 00:32:11,880
but I also have...

582
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:15,630
some personal ties with her,

583
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:21,140
which makes it inconvenient for me
to leave.

584
00:32:25,830 --> 00:32:27,690
Miss, you and the Crown Prince...

585
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:29,640
How come you and a guard...

586
00:32:33,030 --> 00:32:34,430
I'm not a refined person.

587
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:35,640
I don't understand

588
00:32:35,640 --> 00:32:37,270
all these romantic entanglements of yours.

589
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:38,200
I'll leave

590
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:39,810
this token with you.

591
00:32:40,110 --> 00:32:41,240
If there's anything

592
00:32:41,350 --> 00:32:43,010
concerning the Crown Prince,

593
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:44,680
you can come to my residence at any time.

594
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:45,550
Thank you, General Sun.

595
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,240
I'll take my leave.

596
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,270
General Sun, I'll walk you out.

597
00:32:47,270 --> 00:32:47,960
No need.

598
00:32:48,110 --> 00:32:48,640
No, let me walk you out.

599
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,480
No need.

600
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,240
General Sun,

601
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,640
I'll walk you out.

602
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:59,310
Just as Your Majesty predicted,

603
00:32:59,310 --> 00:33:00,720
General Sun really went to examine

604
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:03,180
the assassin's remains
in the dead of night.

605
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:05,110
However, there was

606
00:33:05,550 --> 00:33:07,310
another group there besides him.

607
00:33:07,310 --> 00:33:08,200
Who else?

608
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,800
Our men failed to catch them.

609
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:14,110
But at this point, aside from Princess Fu,

610
00:33:14,110 --> 00:33:15,440
no one

611
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:17,430
will try to save the Crown Prince.

612
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:22,250
Never mind.

613
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,760
Let her run into a few more setbacks,

614
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:26,110
and she'll fall in line.

615
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,160
I'm just worried

616
00:33:30,070 --> 00:33:31,330
that Princess Fu won't

617
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:33,740
easily agree to marry into Great Yan.

618
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:35,000
Rest assured.

619
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:38,350
Since she came back to save Li Ce,

620
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,900
she will naturally accept the marriage—

621
00:33:43,130 --> 00:33:44,850
as long as we make her

622
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:47,270
an offer she cannot refuse.

623
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,920
Zhuge Yue, wake up.

624
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:10,800
Zhuge Yue.

625
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:11,929
Your Highness, run!

626
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,440
I want you to suffer.

627
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:16,230
I'm willing to spend the rest of my life
fasting and doing good deeds,

628
00:34:16,230 --> 00:34:18,880
asking only that His Majesty
and his beloved may live in happiness.

629
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,280
Our interests are aligned.

630
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:21,650
We can bury our past grudges

631
00:34:21,650 --> 00:34:22,760
and discuss a partnership.

632
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:24,620
If you don't want to marry Yan Xun,

633
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:26,670
you can choose to side with me.

